dct_title_s: Λεμεσός, οδικός & τουριστικός χάρτης πόλης : κλιμακα 1:7.800 : + συγκοινωνιακος χαρτης, ιδανικος για Delivery
dct_description_sm: Title from cover and panel. Cover affixed to map sheet directly over title panel of identical format. Printed in western/eastern segments. Includes notes, street index, hotel directory, location maps. Text, location map, table of contents, publisher's map list. On verso: Lemesós synkoinōniakos chartēs - Limassol transportation map.
